 />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 瘋狂文宣輸出</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 佢話， 其實大家要認清楚敵人係共產黨， 嗰啲乜乜77警察、建制派全部都係共產黨啲人。 大家一定要用共產黨最怕嘅嘢去攻擊佢， 而呢樣嘢就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">思想革命</span>， 當年共產黨就係用呢招呃咗班低下層， 先打得贏國民黨。 而當年五四運動， 都係在於民眾思想改變， 共產黨先可以吹到大雞， 班馬上位。 所以佢而家最驚歷史重現。 所以大家唔好少睇文宣， 呢一招可能係我哋最大嘅武器。 勇武固然重要， 等政府知道我哋唔好恰， 但係文宣就係之後嘅超必。<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家呢幾排喺連登唔好再推埋曬啲膠文， 笑七警察乜乜乜。 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推多啲文宣出去， 煲大721，811， 最好推上大陸[size=6]<br />\n<br />\n[size=6]五大訴求，缺一不可</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:20:06.000Z","msg":"佢話， 當年64會失敗， 好大原因係對低下層嘅文輸出唔夠， 淨係得知識分子出嚟而佢哋只係小數。而當年五四會成功， <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">就係因為共產黨識得洗班農民階層嘅腦， 而佢哋係佔大多數。</span> </span><span style=\"color: violet;\">所以今次文宣要集中基層</span>度。 即使<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新移民都唔好放過</span></span>， <span style=\"font-size: large;\">佢哋落嚟香港都係為咗離開大陸， 如果而家同佢講香港就快變成大陸， 睇下佢哋制唔制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"3048eb59efe9a2cbfdd0723320ddf99116578e62","tid":1459243,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:22:14.000Z","msg":"所以啲文宣真係要對準audience，淺黃中立淺藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da9b3658eebf0a178aeb68f506f1c038488414e","tid":1459243,"uid":223986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3048eb59efe9a2cbfdd0723320ddf99116578e62","tid":1459243,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:22:14.000Z","msg":"所以啲文宣真係要對準audience，淺黃中立淺藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:23:29.000Z","msg":"true true true"},{"pid":"e60e50e6b3b0e107a16f7f50d119495034e1f8de","tid":1459243,"uid":291168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ec235e8f1898c9ed1dd2f4e28255740c5493d4a","tid":1459243,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:26:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>不嬲都支持方便人地翻牆睇多Ｄ</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26cb9bef68f542bd747e751c2dff81129a342dfc","tid":1459243,"uid":13695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:26:22.000Z","msg":"如果勇武係槍<br />\n文宣就係好好backup既盾"},{"pid":"a86b587735f5603168cea737318c4351c32eeff0","tid":1459243,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"以文宣義<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">811警暴連環<br />\n⒈蓄意謀殺女救護員 影片直證<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>布袋鉛彈</strong></span>爆眼球 永久失明 面骨碎裂、<br />\n⒉插贜竹枝 <strong>造偽證</strong> 誣陷被捕者、<br />\n⒊地鐡<strong>站內 水平發射催淚彈</strong>CS神經毒氣、<br />\n⒋警<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">喬裝示威者 發動衝擊</span></strong>縱火、<br />\n⒌普通話<strong>軍人 多處滲透</strong>武統、<br />\n⒍<strong>一米內行刑 掃射</strong>胡椒彈、<br />\n⒎<strong>縱容黑幫</strong>橫行 毆打記者路人、<br />\n⒏濫暴<strong>痛毆 重創被捕者</strong> 打掉門牙 血肉模糊、<br />\n⒐屋村<strong>老人民居 發射催淚彈</strong>CS神經毒氣 直噴胡椒屋苑保安</span>"},{"pid":"4df70b2527d29b52d9a68b860dbdf84306ac164d","tid":1459243,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:29:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"826a48d96aae30c5fd28f386587d34953b8bb95f","tid":1459243,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:31:01.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582372c37b871fda3b52d1806c49a67efc59c4c2","tid":1459243,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:31:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"65be0e6ce3eaaafd27b6806282a1d7a63a20ba38","tid":1459243,"uid":282587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:33:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f328d9da4bad47e9d92a79dcc7797dee3e4570b","tid":1459243,"uid":80592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:34:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n文宣戰好撚重要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n所有<span style=\"color: red;\">行動</span>都需要<span style=\"color: red;\">宣傳</span><br />\n要<span style=\"color: red;\">反制國家宣傳機器</span><br />\n唔好咁容易信<span style=\"color: red;\">假消息</span><br />\n要話俾世界知我哋咁做嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">原因</span><br />\n喺文宣 網絡世界都要 <span style=\"color: red;\">Be humble</span><br />\n做事手法好重要<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">811</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">721</span>嘅事一定要俾全世界知<br />\n<br />\n記者日日問721 811<br />\n831 五大訴求真普選百萬大遊行<br />\n要撐到9月搞大罷課<br />\n</div></strong></span><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">雖然抗爭時間久了，但絕對不能忘記，\n我們一直以來的理念，一定要堅持下去。</code></pre><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">繼續大力做藍絲文宣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做事手法好重要<br />\n要反制國家宣傳機器 文宣要大大力做<br />\n對內：AirDrop同路人 行動 戰略 方向 打氣<br />\n對外：Facebook 假acc<span style=\"color: red;\">扮中立</span>拉攏藍絲<br />\nWhatsApp放<span style=\"color: red;\">分化</span>藍絲嘅圖<br />\n用返<span style=\"color: red;\">煽情</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">假消息</span>老點佢哋<br />\n地鐵站貼文宣 播片<br />\n國際：機場派外文文宣 播英文片<br />\n最新可以派埋文宣USB<br />\nQR Code 無用 無人會scan<br />\n</div></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DrLgUUu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrLgUUu.png&h=6550a2e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28K11o3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28K11o3.png&h=985d7652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">冷靜思考 謀求對策</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">對準政權 勿生雜念</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n</div></strong>"},{"pid":"40b457cfe679c8f9c55af42403f2c11cf5491113","tid":1459243,"uid":28123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96c3db3684db8a0d7d67a2c5e679d96ab8ff518","tid":1459243,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:36:40.000Z","msg":"[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a><br />\n幫手支持廣獨，將革命思想傳入中國！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nZFbOE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nZFbOE.png&h=4fd8318f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴打可以用下面條link去印，set左a5 size<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2y1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=c350e2a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR</a>"},{"pid":"faf99e786145529eee367883e1b955693876bda2","tid":1459243,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:37:18.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n文宣最近唔夠力<br />\n無論對外國勢力定中立撚"},{"pid":"cd5510a194a4a47beb0649e3daef9f8e2293e575","tid":1459243,"uid":275202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply